high_descs: Turn around turn right then turn right to the bed.
Pick the soapbar from the bed.
Turn around head towards the sink.
Put the soapbar in the sink, pour the water and take it back.
Turn around turn right go straight near to the shelf.
Place the soapbar on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Pick the SoapBar from the bed and Place the SoapBar in the Shelf

high_descs:
Turn around and walk to the bathtub to your left  bed 
Pick up the soap  bar  in  between the other two.
Turn around and head to the sink across the room.
Put the soap  bar in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Head to the shelf rack to your left.
Put the  soap  bar on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the soap  bar  in  between the other two  and  Put the  soap  bar on the top shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the bed
Pick up soap bar from the bed
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the sink on your right
Place soap bar inside the sink and then take it out
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the shelf
Place soap bar on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Washing soap bar on the sink and placing it on shelf
